  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in the tava-griddle over medium heat.",
    "Add the small onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the medium carrots and cook for another 4 minutes, until they begin to soften.",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook for 5 minutes, until they release their moisture and start to brown.",
    "Add the warm water, long-grain rice, lemon juice, and dill weed. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid and fluff the pilaf with a fork. Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
